    <p>Gov­ern­ing: A Sin­ga­pore Per­spec­tive is pub­lished by The Straits Times Press and is avail­able at lead­ing book­stores at $35 (in­clu­sive of GST).</p>
    <p>The book can also be or­dered from The Straits Times Press on­line book­store at www.stbooks.sg from to­day. The Ama­zon Kin­dle e-book is priced at US$16.99 (S$22.90).</p>
    <p>Prof Jayaku­mar is do­nat­ing his roy­al­ties from the book to the Min­istry of For­eign Af­fair’s adopted charity The Rain­bow Cen­tre, which sup­ports chil­dren with de­vel­op­men­tal and learn­ing needs.</p>


